Earning & Investment App – Concept Overview
This is a mobile-first earning platform where users can invest small amounts of money and earn daily returns, while also growing their income through a referral system.

How the Earning Model Works
1. User Registration
Users sign up using a referral code (optional but encouraged)
Each user gets a unique referral link

2. Investment System
The platform offers different investment plans (VIP levels)
Each plan includes:
Investment amount
Daily earning
Validity period (e.g., 30 days)
Total return

Example:
Invest: $100
Daily income: $5
Duration: 30 days
Total return: $150

3. Daily Earnings
Once a user invests, they start receiving fixed daily income
Earnings are automatically added to their account balance

4. Referral Income
Users can invite others using their referral link
They earn commissions when their referrals invest

This creates a network-based earning model

5. Wallet System
There are two balances:
Available Balance → for investing again
Withdraw Balance → for withdrawing money

6. Deposit & Withdrawal
Users can deposit funds (e.g., crypto like USDT)
Withdraw earnings after reaching minimum limits

7. Admin Control
Admin manages:
Users & approvals
Investment plans
Withdraw requests
Bonuses & commissions
